{"tid":845823,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"索爆媽媽 BLAKE LIVELY的8個瘦身心機","createTime":"2018-10-03T03:25:23.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-03T13:46:09.000Z","uid":160977,"like":0,"dislike":2,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"d8afd969fe8ea68350adc281167ccd6f6b0a8747","tid":845823,"uid":160977,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T03:25:23.000Z","msg":"在《小心幫忙》裡飾演索爆人妻的 Blake Lively，在電影中經常展示 fit 爆身材，差點讓人忘記她已經是兩個小孩的媽媽！懷孕期間她曾增磅超過 60 磅，但很快經過均衡飲食和運動已經回復苗條身材。今日就看看 Blake Lively 的8個瘦身心機！<br />\n<br />\n1. 從不計算卡路里<br />\n <br />\nBlake Lively 從不計算卡路里。相反，她已經訓練了自己的新陳代謝，更能有效地燃燒脂肪。如果一個人的熱量不足，限制著卡路里，會出現反效果。<br />\n2. 自己煮嘢食<br />\n <br />\nBlake 經常自己煮飯，因為想自己做主導控制營養的攝取，從準備食材到烹調，Blake 都會親手包辦。Blake 和老公 Ryan 都喜歡到超市買餸，他們非常注意進入體內的營養和食物。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://bit.ly/2OyDcZv\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fbit.ly%2F2OyDcZv&d=JZQYb0fUoqidTPqKsRS3AqWGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=7b88a0a3\" target=\"_blank\">http://bit.ly/2OyDcZv</a>"},{"pid":"e7c8f86eeef97e0555da44518bb867e8696353b1","tid":845823,"uid":9502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:16:01.000Z","msg":"Gossip girl <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2331022c3e671690578c3e3bcba49600b6adb866","tid":845823,"uid":99700,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:40:06.000Z","msg":"瘦身心機係咩意思"},{"pid":"69c709badcdb51f348b265716ae4614ac906ff15","tid":845823,"uid":3443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T04:56:44.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d424a3b732dae1f8b28920c0c620d385b81c69d","tid":845823,"uid":63641,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-03T06:04:45.000Z","msg":"心得"},{"pid":"13b81937b5223c9be97f5089e4fe7ec603ca5611","tid":845823,"uid":5623